      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/37/9",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنْ رَجُلٍ يَكُونُ لَهُ اَلْمَمْلُوكُونَ فَيُوصِي بِعِتْقِ ثُلُثِهِمْ قَالَ \"كَانَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يُسْهِمُ بَيْنَهُمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3396 - Hariz narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim, who said:\n\"I asked Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about a man who has slaves and wills to free one-third of them.\nImam (as) said: 'Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) used to draw lots among them.'\""
        ]
      }
    },
